    A range of Durations. Like all ranges, it is immutable and its span always includes a minimum of one value.

    Construct using one of the static methods (inclusive(java.time.Duration, java.time.Duration), exclusive(java.time.Duration, java.time.Duration)),

    or by using from(java.time.Duration): 

     DurationRange.from(Duration.ZERO).to(Duration.ofDays(10))      // inclusive upper bound
 DurationRange.from(Duration.ZERO).until(Duration.ofDays(10))   // exclusive upper bound
